languages.text: «La estación que vio crecer a la Navegante ha muerto. La nave insignia de{mf|l| la} Domin es ahora su hogar, y no hay vuelta atrás».
languages.original_text: "The station that nurtured the Navigator is dead. The Domin's flagship is now your home, and there is no way back."

languages.text: 「航宙士を育てたステーションは死滅しました。ドミンの旗艦が新たな家となり、もう戻ることはできません」
languages.original_text: "The station that nurtured the Navigator is dead. The Domin's flagship is now your home, and there is no way back."

languages.text: “那座培养导航者的星站已经死了。如今，秘者的旗舰就是你新的家园，已经无路可退了。”
languages.original_text: "The station that nurtured the Navigator is dead. The Domin's flagship is now your home, and there is no way back."

languages.text: "Die Station, die den Navigator nährte, ist tot. Das Flaggschiff {mf|des|der} Domin ist nun Euer Zuhause, und es gibt kein Zurück."
languages.original_text: "The station that nurtured the Navigator is dead. The Domin's flagship is now your home, and there is no way back."

languages.text: « La station qui a abrité le navigateur n'est plus. Le vaisseau amiral {mf|du|de la} Domin est désormais votre foyer. Il n'y a pas de retour possible. »
